"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Trump says something wonderful can happen before his deadline of 20:00 on Tuesday for Iran to reopen the Strait of Hormuz.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump's Hope for Iran\",            \"translated_version\": \"Trump dice que algo bueno puede pasar antes de su fecha l\u00edmite de las 20:00 el martes para que Ir\u00e1n reabra el Estrecho de Ormuz.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Esperanza de Trump para Ir\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"No Israeli diplomats are in Turkey, and the Istanbul consulate has been empty for two-and-a-half years.\",            \"english_title\": \"Empty Consulate in Turkey\",            \"translated_version\": \"No hay diplom\u00e1ticos israel\u00edes en Turqu\u00eda, y el consulado en Estambul ha estado vac\u00edo por dos a\u00f1os y medio.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Consulado Vac\u00edo en Turqu\u00eda\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel's military says troops fired at a vehicle driven by a Palestinian because they thought it was a threat.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Troops Fire\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de Israel dice que los soldados dispararon a un veh\u00edculo conducido por un palestino porque pensaron que era una amenaza.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Soldados Israel\u00edes Disparan\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"US Vice-President JD Vance supports Orb\u00e1n in Budapest.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Support for Orb\u00e1n\",            \"translated_version\": \"El vicepresidente de EE.UU., JD Vance, apoya a Orb\u00e1n en Budapest.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Apoyo de EE.UU. a Orb\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Vietnam's communist party chief is now also the country's president, which is unusual because it gives him a lot of power.\",            \"english_title\": \"Vietnam's Powerful Leader\",            \"translated_version\": \"El jefe del partido comunista de Vietnam ahora tambi\u00e9n es el presidente del pa\u00eds, lo cual es raro porque le da mucho poder.\",            \"translated_title\": \"L\u00edder Poderoso de Vietnam\"        }    ]}"